### =========================================================================
### 1. MULTI-USER REGISTRATION (Run once to populate DB)
### =========================================================================

# @name RegisterOwner
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alex@reform.app",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "username": "Alex Owner"
}

###

# @name RegisterMember1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bob@reform.app",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "username": "Bob Collaborator"
}

###

